Author: idiotvegan
Text: i don’t know exactly what to say because i’ve been in your exact situation and sometimes it feels like absolutely nothing anyone can say or do would help. but you deserve to eat, you deserve to have food and energy, and if it makes you feel better then i give you express permission to eat what sounds and feels good, including a cookie. you’re a wonderful amazing super badass person and i know you can fight this

Author: NeuntyNeun
Text: Little addition bread is now my FEAR food and the fact that I ate probably 200 calories worth of a wrap plus 200 calories of falafels makes me crave death
